title: Muse - Live at Glastonbury (inc. Citizen Erased & Stockholm Synd
description:
This is the audio from the Muse Live At Glastonbury DVD ****PLUS**** the two tracks played at that gig that weren't included on the DVD. I'm not sure but i think this is probably the most complete version of this gig on here. Top notch sound quality aswell ;)

Set List:

1. Hysteria
2. New Born
3. Sing For Absolution
4. Muscle Museum
5. Citizen Erased
6. Apocalypse Please
7. Ruled By Secrecy
8. Sunburn
9. Butterflies And Hurricanes
10. Bliss
11. Time Is Running Out
12. Plug In Baby
13. Blackout
14. Stockholm Syndrome
